Considerations for Connected Data Sources

Selecting Connection Fields

Faceting only works on fields used to define the connection. For example, the StageName field is used in a connection, so faceting works with it.

Connecting Date Fields

When using date fields, use time periods that describe the top-level date field. Create a filter widget with a time period and update the dashboard JSON to include this time period.
